      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHIMA SAND (1) sizzled around 340m in 19.23 when winning a Grade 5 at Hobart last start. Expected to go close again if runs up to latest time. SWEET SUNDOWN (5) turned in a plain run last time when sixth at The Meadows over 525m behind Keep Rolling (30.73) in a Grade 5. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from four starts. Should be in this for a long way. OUR MISS MAGGIE (2) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish third (16.42) at this track in a Grade 5 over 278m. Expecting another good run. PINAROO FLYER (8) hit the frame here last start and can sneak into the finish again.",
